name: School to Prison Pipeline
description:
This is a depiction of the battle to get an education, when the system is broken, and the ways out are surrounding by . . . stacks of information or prison bars. Freedom or the yard? Many ways out and lots of views of what lies on the other side. 

For the teachers who love the students, and want more for their future, this was created at my last night of work at a Baltimore inner city school. 
Gan Art - Text to image AI generations - Library stacks, inner city blues, and school to prison pipeline. This is the final image of 2000 renderings.
